slides.title: Unconnected nodes
slides.text: Here we see the ring of unconnected nodes around the main network, 33 websites in total.

slides.title: Broad range of actors
slides.text: The unconnected nodes appear to express a range of the different actor types.

slides.title: Some actors not represented
slides.text: However, some actors are not represented in the ring of unconnected nodes. These include the governmental organizations and the patient organizations. In addition, we only see one actor from the category 'other' represented.
